title: Proposal to lower BUNNY emissions for all pools (excluding BUNNY Boost and BUNNY-BNB Boost)
body: We propose to decrease the minting rate for BUNNY from 5 BUNNY per BNB to 3 BUNNY per BNB.  The protocol reserves 30% of yields to distribute to users as a profit share through the Bunny Pool. This amount is called the Bunny Distribution. Whereas currently the protocol mints 5 BUNNY per BNB of the Bunny Distribution, we propose to reduce the rate to 3 BUNNY per BNB.
choices: YES, reduce to 3 BUNNY per BNB
author: 0xe87f02606911223C2Cf200398FFAF353f60801F7
